Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/earthquake">Earthquake</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/earthquake">Earthquake</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The user sets off an earthquake that hits all the Pokemon in the battle.</p>